{"endpoint": "opencode-go", "test_id": "code_sort", "category": "code_gen", "test_name": "快速排序实现", "run_index": 2, "success": true, "error": "", "ttft_ms": 9928.59, "total_ms": 10022.66, "generation_ms": 94.07, "input_tokens": 103, "output_tokens": 831, "tps": 8833.72, "response_text": "```python\ndef quicksort(arr):\n    if len(arr) <= 1:\n        return arr\n    pivot = arr[len(arr) // 2]\n    left = [x for x in arr if x < pivot]\n    middle = [x for x in arr if x == pivot]\n    right = [x for x in arr if x > pivot]\n    return quicksort(left) + middle + quicksort(right)\n```", "quality_passed": true, "quality_score": 1.0, "quality_note": "排序正确"}
